Write a professional cover letter for this job application.

Candidate:
- Name: {{ user.name }}
- Email: {{ user.email }}
- Experience: {{ user.years_of_experience }} years
- Skills: {{ user.skills | join(', ') if user.skills else 'General' }}
- Education: {{ user.education | join(', ') if user.education else 'Not specified' }}
- Summary: {{ user.summary }}

Job:
- Title: {{ job.title }}
- Company: {{ job.company }}
- Description: {{ job.description[:1500] }}
- Requirements: {{ job.requirements[:10] | join(', ') }}
- Matched Skills: {{ matched_skills | join(', ') }}
- Missing Skills: {{ missing_skills[:5] | join(', ') }}

{% if rag_context %}
## Insights from Past Applications to Similar Roles:
{{ rag_context }}
{% endif %}

Guidelines:
- Keep it to 3-4 paragraphs
- Be specific about why this company/role is interesting
- Highlight matched skills with concrete examples
- Address any skill gaps positively (eager to learn)
- Professional but personable tone
- Do NOT include placeholders like [Company Address]
